questiondata.strat-other: I used acronyms and grouping to make the task easier. I am also a synesthete, so I thought of ways to connect my senses to create mental pictures and associations. I do mental exercises daily to help strengthen my remembering and try to create a semi-eidetic memory, so that helped me in this task, too.
